{"tid":1525916,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"GANKER EX 格鬥機械人","createTime":"2019-09-01T03:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T03:33:36.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"56f2d0574edeb2fef81721afabd5059c0ff8c327","tid":1525916,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2019/08/31/237548/wnfp033p02a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2019%2F08%2F31%2F237548%2Fwnfp033p02a.jpg&h=80b7483d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2019/08/31/237548/wnfp033p02b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2019%2F08%2F31%2F237548%2Fwnfp033p02b.jpg&h=0e384fde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■從包裝盒取出的GANKER EX只是一副骨架，並未裝上盔甲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2019/08/31/237548/wnfp033p02c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2019%2F08%2F31%2F237548%2Fwnfp033p02c.jpg&h=c2924f40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2019/08/31/237548/wnfp033p02d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2019%2F08%2F31%2F237548%2Fwnfp033p02d.jpg&h=c8574659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■利用3D打印機為機械人DIY盔甲及武器。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2019/08/31/237548/wnfp033p02e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2019%2F08%2F31%2F237548%2Fwnfp033p02e.jpg&h=04fd46c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■人偶控制器將操控感大為提升，非手機熒幕可比擬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2019/08/31/237548/wnfp033p02f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2019%2F08%2F31%2F237548%2Fwnfp033p02f.jpg&h=8a724124&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■年底將會加推附有體感控制器的版本。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2019/08/31/237548/wnfp033p02g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2019%2F08%2F31%2F237548%2Fwnfp033p02g.jpg&h=46d841ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■對戰時可於App查看哪處被擊中及扣血量。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2019/08/31/237548/wnfp033p02h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2019%2F08%2F31%2F237548%2Fwnfp033p02h.jpg&h=9ff85316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■下盤四足均裝有摩打，輕易帶來三百六十度急速轉向。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2019/08/31/237548/wnfp033p02i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2019%2F08%2F31%2F237548%2Fwnfp033p02i.jpg&h=53525388&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■最大樂趣來自與同道中人在擂台上對決。<br />\n<br />\n身穿控制裝置遙控機械人，已不是電影情節，現實中也可以在腰間佩戴造型獨特的控制器，然後操控擂台上的格鬥機械人──GANKER EX，如影隨形般使出絕技，將對手擊倒，箇中樂趣非一般電子格鬥遊戲可比擬。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>關節靈活　高速移動</strong><br />\n<br />\n由GJS（工匠社）開發的GANKER EX，屬第三代格鬥機械人，骨架穿上全套盔甲後戰鬥風格強烈，事實機身構造經過改良，上身為仿人體的九個關節設計，兩臂可做出複雜動作，舉高、垂低，又或屈曲、伸展，甚至交叉擋格，活動自由度十足，毫無傳統機械人那種僵硬感，速度亦可達0.09/60度。至於格鬥最重要的下盤，此機沿用四足系統，可做出三百六十度無死角的急速轉向，最高速度達5米/秒，加上九軸底盤系統，可以自動校準路線，空間走位更加準確。另一大改良在於控制器，新作採用嶄新的人偶控制器，既可以吸盤置於枱面，也可拉出伸縮帶將控制器扣於腰間，然後手握兩支操控桿，即可同步控制機械人做出不同動作及方位移動。由於控制器與機械人經由5GHz WiFi連接，除了訊號連接穩定，配合空間定位技術，反應快至毫秒，有助人機動作同步。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>扣血分勝負　DIY盔甲</strong><br />\n<br />\n既然是格鬥機械人，最大樂趣當然是與另一台GANKER EX在擂台對決。為讓比賽真實反映勝負，機械人內置七個電子計分部位，分別位於頭、肩、胸、手及背，可以偵測對方攻擊，一旦擊中會被扣血，控制器亦會震動及以燈效通知，要是血量由1,000減至0，則代表戰敗。要提升GANKER EX戰鬥力，除了練習操控技巧，還可以自行改裝盔甲及武器，甚至利用3D打印機DIY。由於機械人的手部設有訊號插口，玩家可以創造發光、旋轉，甚至發射的獨門武器，殺對手一個措手不及。說起個人化，玩家亦可以把GANKER EX看成高達一類模型，為機身及盔甲上色，可見撇開擂台爭勝，閒時亦帶來不少樂趣。值得一提的是，GANKER EX現時推出的是人偶控制器版，查實廠方還開發了體感控制器，藉着穿在身上的多組感應器，與機械人做出更協調的動作，預計年底推出。<br />\n<br />\nGANKER EX<br />\n<br />\n控制器：人偶控制器<br />\n<br />\n連接方式：5GHz WiFi<br />\n<br />\n專用App：《GANKER EX》<br />\n<br />\n電池容量：2,000mAh（可拆式）<br />\n<br />\n體積/重量：222&times;251&times;197mm/1,375g<br />\n<br />\n售價：$2,398<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/ls/792545/%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E5%89%AF%E5%88%8A-GANKER-EX-%E6%A0%BC%E9%AC%A5%E6%A9%9F%E6%A2%B0%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fls%2F792545%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%2589%25AF%25E5%2588%258A-GANKER-EX-%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A2%25B0%25E4%25BA%25BA&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8bxT9vY2lxR77dvs0GIZdErU%3D&h=5826e0a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fls%2F792545%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%2589%25AF%25E5%2588%258A-GANKER-EX-%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A2%25B0%25E4%25BA%25BA&h=c151f6d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/ls/792545/%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E5%89%AF%E5%88%8A-GANKER-EX-%E6%A0%BC%E9%AC%A5%E6%A9%9F%E6%A2%B0%E4%BA%BA</a>"}]}